videos.headline: Jaxson Robinson hits dagger 3 for BYU
videos.description: Jaxson Robinson puts BYU up eight late in the second half as he puts in the 3-pointer from the wing.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jaxson Robinson hits dagger 3 for BYU) 2024/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU shines from 3-point line in top-25 win over Baylor
videos.description: BYU knocks down 14 3-pointers as the Cougars pick up the home win over No. 11 Baylor.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (BYU shines from 3-point line in top-25 win over Baylor) 2024/02/20 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Jalen Bridges puts Baylor up 8-0 with a dunk
videos.description: Baylor goes up 8-0 early as Jalen Bridges gets the steal and slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jalen Bridges puts Baylor up 8-0 with a dunk) 2024/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU's Fousseyni Traore pins his defender for and-1
videos.description: BYU big man Fousseyni Traore pins his defender under the basket and converts the and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (BYU's Fousseyni Traore pins his defender for and-1) 2024/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jalen Bridges quiets the crowd by banking in 3
videos.description: Jalen Bridges puts Baylor up four as he banks in a 3-pointer from the wing.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jalen Bridges quiets the crowd by banking in 3) 2024/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dallin Hall's 3 has BYU fans hyped
videos.description: BYU forces a Baylor timeout as Dallin Hall hits the 3-pointer for the Cougars' first lead of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dallin Hall's 3 has BYU fans hyped) 2024/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Yves Missi ends half in style with alley-oop dunk on defender
videos.description: Baylor ends the half with a huge alley-oop dunk from Yves Missi on a defender.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Yves Missi ends half in style with alley-oop dunk on defender) 2024/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aly Khalifa splashes his fourth 3-pointer of the night
videos.description: Aly Khalifa steps behind the line and knocks it down from long range for his fourth 3-pointer of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Aly Khalifa splashes his fourth 3-pointer of the night) 2024/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Former BYU player Caleb Lohner gets booed after throwing down dunk
videos.description: Baylor's Caleb Lohner throws down the dunk and gets booed by the fans from his former school.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Former BYU player Caleb Lohner gets booed after throwing down dunk) 2024/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jaxson Robinson gives BYU biggest lead of the night with a 3
videos.description: BYU goes up eight as Jaxson Robinson gets the lucky roll on the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jaxson Robinson gives BYU biggest lead of the night with a 3) 2024/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Jalen Bridges impressively finishes transition dunk
videos.description: Baylor's Jalen Bridges goes up and stuffs it home with two hands in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Baylor's Jalen Bridges impressively finishes transition dunk) 2024/02/20 ESHEET
